						<div class="postbody">You can't buy Photoshop anymore because it and other Adobe applications have moved to its Creative Cloud rental platform. Likewise, the PCB design tool <a href="https://soylentnews.org/article.pl?sid=17/01/21/0111238" class="postlink">EAGLE is now rental-only</a>, $100 per year for Standard (2 layers, 160 cm^2) or $500 per year for Premium.<br /><br />Time for an exodus to KiCAD yet?</div>

