					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Not really about Eagle, but...<br />I ranted about Photoshop on some forum, about a year or <br />two ago...<br /><br />For me, they just 'jumped the shark'. <br /><br />Two major reasons.<br />- There is really no innovation any more. I was using a version of Photoshop from 10 years ago, and it's only downside was a lack of animating gifs tools<br />- there are dozens of free softwares that do a nearly identical job<br /><br />The only problem you get, is, it's a pain to open a Photoshop file .psd in GIMP. There is a website that can convert the file to a GIMP file.</div>

					
